@owner: PaymentsTeam
@stability: stable
@since: 2024-09-01
@reviewed: 2026-04-02

Feature: Payment Gateway
  "Charges and refunds against a third-party payment processor."

  Provides:
    - PaymentGateway.charge(token, amount) -> ChargeResult
    - PaymentGateway.refund(charge_id, amount) -> RefundResult

  Scenario (happy-path): Successful charge
    Given a valid payment token and a positive amount
    When charge is invoked
    Then a ChargeResult with status 'captured' is returned

  Scenario (negative): Declined card
    Given a token whose underlying card declines
    When charge is invoked
    Then it MUST raise PaymentError
